data.description: Welcome home - just in time for the holidays!! Nestled at the end of a serene cul-de-sac, this 4-bedroom home is a versatile gem. It features a ground-floor bedroom, separate full bath, three additional bedrooms upstairs, and a convenient laundry area. The loft area is perfect for movie nights! The kitchen is a chef's dream with a gas stove, and granite countertops. The spacious backyard is a blank canvas for your outdoor oasis and play area. This home offers style, comfort, and endless possibilities. Come see this Magnolia Park home today! Interior has been freshly painted.
